INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(156, 1, '2015-04-05 18:07:10', '2015-04-05 18:07:10', 'Weaving a rich dream, Suneet Varma\r\nArmed with a degree from Europe, extensive international experience and exposure, and a deep love for couture, Suneet Varma is known for his exquisite creations. India’s foremost couturier talks to Jayshree A Mulherkar on his inspirations, fashion and bridal trends. He even doles out some priceless bridal tips.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong> <a href="http://ucantest.com/haute-brides/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1000X653-Suneet-Varma-1-401.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-263 size-full" src="http://ucantest.com/haute-brides/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1000X653-Suneet-Varma-1-401.png" alt="1000X653 Suneet Varma 1 (40)" width="1000" height="653" /></a></strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWith his sartorial style that exudes elegance, sophistication and feminity for today’s modern woman, Suneet has captured all with his breathtaking collections through the years. An alumnus of the London School of Fashion, he started with studying sculpting  and painting, but soon switched to fashion designing. Today, he is one of the most celebrated designers and recently, presented an awe-inspiring collection inspired by the gorgeous traditional motifs and crafts of Gujarat, Rajasthan, Punjab and South India, the clothes were utterly romantic, feminine and flirtatious at the Lakmé Fashion Week Summer/Resort 2015.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHis summer bridal collection called ‘Decorative Arts of India’ presented by Reliance Jewels, was a riot of colour, with shades of red – <em>Sindoor</em>, vermillion, <em>gulaal</em>, fuchsia, pink rose and magenta, which were splashed with large mirror work borders in thread embroidery. Emphasising on the rich crafts of the country, Suneet added white and ivory with tonal <em>aari</em> work, deep navy and cobalt blue with antique gold and copper touches to the designs. Silk, rich velvet, chiffon, tulle, jacquard, georgette and lush traditional textiles were the fabrics he used beautifully to bring out what’s best for today’s bride. Besides, sheer net <em>sarees</em> dazzled with grey and oyster pearls splashed with Swarovski Crystals.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a title="Membership Checkout" href="http://ucantest.com/haute-brides/membership-account/membership-checkout/?level=1">Read more here:</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Confessions of a Couturier', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'confessions-of-a-couturier', '', '', '2015-04-26 20:30:17', '2015-04-26 20:30:17', '', 0, 'http://ucantest.com/haute-brides/?p=156', 0, 'post', '', 0);
