INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(182, 1, '2015-04-05 19:01:54', '2015-04-05 19:01:54', 'Think of Dubai and the first thing that springs to mind is shopping, sandy beaches, the vibrant nightlife, adventure sports, and much more. Yes, there’s lots to explore besides, this being a great destination for your honeymoon too! HB&amp;H fills you in on why Dubai for your romantic sojourn.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\nSituated on the South West corner of the Arabian Gulf and Eastern Coast of the Arabian Peninsula, Dubai is a beautiful blend of traditional and contemporary. The second largest of the seven Emirates that consist of the UAE, it certainly has an edge over most of its neighbouring cities. A city that has sunshine all year round, it offers a variety of activities to keep you well entertained. So, embark on an exciting journey and indulge yourself with your love, in this sun soaked city full of adventure.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>The Bastakia Quarter</strong> – If you are a history buff, this is one site you need to head to for that fix of old world romantic charm. It is one of the original places that was established by Iranians in Dubai and was earlier known as Persian quarter. One of the most picturesque heritage sites, the Bastakia Quarter or the Bur Bastakia located between Bur Dubai and the Dubai Creek. It is like a mini maze and houses several cafes and art galleries. Right from contemporary art at XVA Gallery to Middle Eastern art at Majlis Gallery, you have it all here. Then, go exploring the Dubai Museum and take back a slice of history, culture and tradition with you.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a title="Subscription Now" href="http://ucantest.com/haute-brides/sample-page/subscription-now/">Read more here:</a>', 'Delightful Dubai   ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'delightful-dubai', '', '', '2015-04-24 15:56:54', '2015-04-24 15:56:54', '', 0, 'http://ucantest.com/haute-brides/?p=182', 0, 'post', '', 0);
